Class com.box.androidlib.DAO.DAO extends java.lang.Object implements Serializable

serialVersionUID: 1L

Serialized Fields

mDAOCreated

long mDAOCreated
The local timestamp in milliseconds, that the DAO was created. This initially gets set at construction using Java.util.Date.getTime().

mDAOUpdated

long mDAOUpdated
The local timestamp in milliseconds of the last time the DAO was updated. The library currently doesn't ever use this, but the field is included for developers to use.
